<item>
            <title>[QPID-327] [race condition] PoolingFilter : Possible race condition when completing a Job</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-327</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the following code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    //Job.JobCompletionHandler&lt;br/&gt;
    public void completed(IoSession session, Job job)&lt;br/&gt;
    {&lt;br/&gt;
        if (job.isComplete())&lt;br/&gt;
        {&lt;br/&gt;
            job.release();&lt;br/&gt;
            if (!job.isReferenced())&lt;/p&gt;
            {
                _jobs.remove(session);
            }
&lt;p&gt;        }&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Another thread could acquire() the job between the call to job.isReferenced() and _jobs.remove(session);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
